236
00:13:26,167 --> 00:13:28,266
kenapa kau tidak langsung memberitahuku seperti seorang pria sejati?

237
00:13:28,267 --> 00:13:30,967
Benar.

238
00:13:34,267 --> 00:13:36,266
Baik, kita akan mendekati pria itu,

239
00:13:36,267 --> 00:13:38,367
