Kurasa waktunya aku pergi.

256
00:14:40,875 --> 00:14:42,675
Ayo kita pergi ke tempat berikut.

257
00:14:50,175 --> 00:14:52,175
Apa itu? Astaga.

258
00:15:09,975 --> 00:15:11,374
Ke mana perginya dia?

259
00:15:11,375 --> 00:15:14,174
Tidak apa-apa. Dia ada di sana.

260
00:15:14,175 --> 00:15:16,174
Benar!

261
00:15:16,175 --> 00:15:17,274
Dia duduk.

262
00:15:17,275 --> 00:15:19,074
Kita akan segera mulai

263
00:15:19,075 --> 00:15:21,474
