Jangan harap.

292
00:17:21,375 --> 00:17:24,174
Tidakkah kau dengar suara lain selain kembang api itu barusan?

293
00:17:24,175 --> 00:17:26,075
Ya, aku mendengarnya. Itu seperti suara "bang"!

294
00:17:31,975 --> 00:17:33,374
Yakura!

295
00:17:33,375 --> 00:17:34,375
Nn. Sato!

296
00:17:34,376 --> 00:17:36,174
Apa yang sedang kau lakukan? Ayo kita kejar dia!

297
00:17:36,175 --> 00:17:37,175
Baik!

298
00:17:47,675 --> 00:17:50,474
Inspektur, mereka berdua sedang mengejar Yakura.

299
00:17:50,475 --> 00:17:52,374
