309
00:18:51,975 --> 00:18:53,475
Kau takkan lolos!

310
00:19:11,275 --> 00:19:12,575
Cincin itu!

311
00:19:18,475 --> 00:19:19,675
Sial!

312
00:19:38,175 --> 00:19:41,075
Cincinku!

313
00:19:55,775 --> 00:19:58,974
Kau menjalankan tugas dengan bagus, Petugas Takagi.

314
00:19:58,975 --> 00:20:00,974
Inspektur Shiratori?

315
00:20:00,975 --> 00:20:02,474
Apa yang membawamu ke sini?

316
00:20:02,475 --> 00:20:05,374
Yah, kami mendapat petunjuk tentang transaksi narkoba

317
00:20:05,375 --> 00:20:08,274
